連最基本的小學級程度數學 - 投票解決問題，<br />\n都未真係好掌握到。<br />\n<br />\n好似醫學報告，都係搵sample做，唔透明公開，又冇搵big data做analysis，連一個基本俾病友評分的系統都無。"},{"pid":"2aa927a85bcbe23edffa5bf5ecfea792571852e3","tid":2076464,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b64c669629bbeec32549f65368651cf1bc7413c6","tid":2076464,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f62bc86555edf5fb3efe543b12dc44ac27b3bfd","tid":2076464,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbcd47252fa9faa666a0f1a254b5d446f8deef34","tid":2076464,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"唔係唔相信數學<br />\n而係獨裁太爽<br />\n冇可能會肯自願交返個權出嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"公投都係針對一些大爭議的法案做<br />\n唔會影響到佢的權益<br />\n呢樣都唔肯真係........<br />\n另外醫學又仲咩咁多年都冇一個比病友評分的系統？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"因為醫療patient satisfaction意義唔大<br />\n攞factual啲嘅data會好啲<br />\n仲有點解唔公投就係因為撐政府係少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"連大數據都唔信任，patient的經驗又唔信任。"},{"pid":"d88fef374f9ffa890c619a63ce047b13b29d83de","tid":2076464,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2aa927a85bcbe23edffa5bf5ecfea792571852e3","tid":2076464,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b64c669629bbeec32549f65368651cf1bc7413c6","tid":2076464,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f62bc86555edf5fb3efe543b12dc44ac27b3bfd","tid":2076464,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"公投都係針對一些大爭議的法案做<br />\n唔會影響到佢的權益<br />\n呢樣都唔肯真係........<br />\n另外醫學又仲咩咁多年都冇一個比病友評分的系統？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"因為醫療patient satisfaction意義唔大<br />\n攞factual啲嘅data會好啲<br />\n仲有點解唔公投就係因為撐政府係少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\